					<![CDATA[
						 <p>There’s pretty much no link between SCP-1953 and SCP-1953-1.<br /> This entry is so busy that by the time I reached the ‘artwork’ addendum, I was so busy trying to piece the components of this article together that I just gave up. You can’t just throw so many different things together without a connection. -1.</p> 
